  "prompt": "Who are some of the best lawyers in India?",
  "response": "India has a diverse legal landscape with many accomplished lawyers known for their expertise in various fields such as constitutional law, corporate law, criminal law, and more. Here are some prominent lawyers who have made significant contributions to the legal profession in India:\n\n1. **Fali S. Nariman** - One of India's most renowned constitutional lawyers, known for his work in public interest litigation and legal advice to various organizations.\n\n2. **Harish Salve** - A leading expert in constitutional law and arbitration, he has represented clients in high-profile cases, including the Indian government in international arbitration matters.\n\n3. **Kapil Sibal** - A former Union Minister and a prominent lawyer with extensive experience in constitutional and civil law.\n\n4. **Abhishek Manu Singhvi** - A senior advocate known for his work in constitutional law, commercial law, and public law, and he often appears before the Supreme Court of India.\n\n5. **Mukul Rohatgi** - A former Attorney General of India, known for his expertise in constitutional, civil, and criminal law.\n\n6. **A. M. Singhvi** - Noted for his skills in litigation and advocacy, particularly in the Supreme Court and various High Courts.\n\n7. **Rakesh Dwivedi** - Renowned for his work in constitutional law and key legal battles involving critical issues.\n\n8. **Indira Jaising** - A prominent senior advocate known for her work in women's rights and human rights law, as well as her involvement in public interest litigation.\n\n9. **Soli Sorabjee** - A former Attorney General of India and a respected senior advocate, known for his constitutional law expertise.\n\n10. **Prashant Bhushan** - A noted lawyer and activist known for his work in public interest litigations, particularly involving governmental accountability.\n\nThese lawyers are recognized for their expertise, experience, and contributions to legal practice in India. Note that this list is not exhaustive, and many other equally talented lawyers also excel in various fields of law.",
